<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">Hackamore is a large volcanic field east of Medicine Lake volcano. This Quaternary field covers an area of at least 850 km2 with at least a dozen vents, the youngest of which is about 600,000 years old (Hildreth, 2007).</p></td></tr>
