<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">A group of cinder cones and lava flows in the Buffalo Valley north of the Oligocene Fish Creek Mountains caldera range in age from 3.05 to 0.92 million years ago (Dohrenwend, in Wood and Kienle 1990).      </p></td></tr>
