<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">The Sentinel Plain volcanic field covers about 600 km2 along the Gila River with basaltic lava flows. The field was active from 3.3 to possibly 1.3 million years ago (Lynch, in Wood and Kienle 1990).</p></td></tr>
