<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">The Springerville Volcanic Field contains more than 380 vents and lava flows of Pliocene to Pleistocene age.  This alkali basalt field contains cinder cones, maars and lava domes, with the youngest dated cones being 0.3 million years ago.</p></td></tr>
