<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">Dawson (1992) considered the age of Sadiman volcano to be uncertain, with one source considering it to be Pleistocene and another obtaining a K-Ar age of 4.5 Ma.  Clasts of Sadiman lavas are found in sediments dated to 1.7-2.0 million years.</p></td></tr>
