<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">In the Chew Bahir basin along the Ethiopia-Kenya border cones of basaltic ejecta surrounded by very recent sediments.  The volcanics are mapped as Quaternary (Davidson, 1983).      </p></td></tr>
