<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">Ali Mela Ale is included in Dubbi line of volcanoes which decrease in age northward (Mohr et al. 1976). Alimelali is next volcano SE of Oyma, which is dated at 0.5 million years ago (CNR-CNRS 1973).</p></td></tr>
