<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">Lahitte et al. (2003b) noted that "Despite poor constraints on timing of emplacement, Undurer and Babb-Olou volcanoes seem to have been more or less contemporaneous, erupting about 2 Myr ago...."</p></td></tr>
