<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">Included in Dubbi line of volcanoes which decrease in age northward (Mohr et al. 1976). Katahelu is approx. 40 km S of Oyma which is dated at 0.5 million years ago (CNR-CNRS, 1973).</p></td></tr>
