<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">This isolated cone surrounded by lava flows about 18 km NE of the southern part of the Harrat al Birk field was considered to be similar in age to Jibal Haylah (54 km N), dated as Pleistocene by Coleman et al. (1983).</p></td></tr>
