<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">Cancajanag is a lava dome complex on Leyte Island, north of Mahagnao volcano on the lower NW flank of Lobi. The age of its most recent eruptions is not known, but it was classified as potentially active by PHIVOLCS.</p></td></tr>
