<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">Ilihan is Quaternary volcano with a lava flow dated at about 1.24 million years lies in SE Leyte Island, north of Cabalían volcano (Sajona et al., 1997). Another undated Quaternary volcano was mapped immediately to the north of Silago.</p></td></tr>
