<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">Jianshan volcano (at the Jianshan Farm) is located NW of the Wudalianchi volcanic field. Zhao and others (2014) reported that this isolated monogenetic cinder cone was K?Ar dated at 0.12 ± 0.02 Ma.</p></td></tr>
