<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">The Raiden-yama volcano complex along the SW coast of Hokkaido consists of  Raiden-yama, Iwanai-dake and Mekunnai-dake volcanoes and was active about 1.4-0.8 million years ago (Nakano et al., 2001-).</p></td></tr>
