<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">Nanashigure volcano is a Pleistocene pyroclastic-flow plateau and lava dome.   Nanashigure-yama was active about 1.1-0.9 million years ago (Nakano et al., 2001-).</p></td></tr>
