<tr><td colspan="2"><p align="justify">Chubetsu volcano (Chubetsu-dake or Tyubetu-dake), an andesitic stratovolcano SE of Daisetsu volcano, was active about 1-0.8 million years ago (Nakano et al., 2001-).</p></td></tr>
